{
  "texts": [
    "A successfully produced 3D coordinates may be utilized directly in further molecular computations, including docking, molecular dynamics, and quantum mechanical simulations.",
    "We foresee this 3D technology being beneficial for AI-driven drug discovery initiatives in the near future, as evidenced by rapid research and fine-tuning of the models for better results.",
    "(Polykovskiy et al., 2018; Kwon et al., 2019; Simonovsky and Komodakis, 2023).",
    "There has been a surge of new GAI models with the development of GANs (Goodfellow et al., 2020).",
    "GANs may be trained to generate synthetic compounds with the required characteristics via an adversarial training procedure."
  ]
}